name: 2014 Limited Edition Calendar
description: The 4th annual calendar from the popular Melbourne Street collection. Featuring 13 of the best photographs from the streets of Melbourne shot by photographer William Watt during 2013. Each page features a square cropped photograph, combined with a clean, minimalist layout, understated typography and important Melbourne events. Each Melbourne Street 2014 Colour Calendar is individually numbered and signed. 20% of proceeds from Calendar sales go directly to Melbourne Street to Home. SIZE A3 // 15 Pages (13 internal + Front and Back Covers) QUALITY The entire calendar is printed on a superbly smooth 310gsm paper stock, giving it a feeling of quality and excellent image reproduction. AUTHENTICATION Calendars are numbered and are signed by the photographer. SHIPPING Ships securely packed flat within 5-10 days of order. Australian orders $6 // International $12 For more information and a full preview of the calendar visit http://melbournestreet.net/2013/10/30/melbourne-street-calendar-2014-preview/ ©2013 Will Watt

name: A0 Giclée prints
description:
All shots from the Melbourne Street website are available as limited edition prints.

Please specify the title of your print in the comments section of your order. If making multiple orders, just list the prints you would like and quantity of each.

SIZE 
A0 // 1189 x 841 mm

QUALITY 
All giclée prints are produced at Michael's Camera store in Elizabeth Street, Melbourne. Prints are made on ILFORD GALERIE GOLD FIBRE SILK, which offers enhanced definition, extended tonal range, and excellent archival properties.

FRAMING/MOUNTING 
I leave an approximately 1-inch border to facilitate framing and mounting. I can help arrange framing at additional cost, just email me after your purchase for a quote.

AUTHENTICATION 
Prints are numbered on a first come first serve basis (ie. the first one sold in a series is #1 of 12), and are signed by the photographer.

Ships packed in mail tube within 5-10 days of order. 
Final print does not feature Melbourne Street watermark.

©2013 William Watt

name: The Melbourne Metre
description:
These spectacular panorama's show the Yarra River at it's finest, with spectacular cloud formations, storms and sunsets brilliantly printed onto Gold Fibre Silk paper by Michael's Camera Store.

All panoramas are printed to exactly 1 metre wide (plus border), perfect as a featured item on a wall.

SIZE 
1 Metre Wide (height varies slightly)

QUALITY 
All giclée prints are produced at Michael's Camera store in Elizabeth Street, Melbourne. Prints are made on ILFORD GALERIE GOLD FIBRE SILK, which offers enhanced definition, extended tonal range, and excellent archival properties.

description:
